							<a href="/article/1809092"><div class="post_thm_bg  post_thm_movie">
								<img src="//static.sanyonews.jp/image/article/size3/9/3/5/1/935176a1e722bba439cd0d917eca4ca5_1.jpg" alt="岡山で民家２棟全焼　けが人なし">
